{"tid":1829154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［西九影相手足］黑警用警槍觸碰被告衣物 令手搶有他衣物纖維","createTime":"2020-01-18T13:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T09:47:08.000Z","uid":22556,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"73843e91989708e2c958683236e943013f78086e","tid":1829154,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:05:57.000Z","msg":"公開大學姓何 23 歲男學生，日前於深水埗西九龍中心美食廣場拍攝時，被指拍攝到休班警員，涉違反法庭禁制令被帶走，警方其後指他涉「普通襲擊」及「藏有攻擊性武器」被捕，一度將他扣查近 48 小時，才准以 7,000 元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n跟進事件的區議員李文浩今透露，何同學於深水埗警署內配合警方要求搜身期間，有警員一度拿出左輪手槍並觸碰他的衣物，試圖令手槍上留有他的衣物纖維，並指「信唔信我告你搶槍同襲警？」有警員又曾從後推何同學的後腦令他鼻子撞牆，及強逼他露出笑容等。<br />\n<br />\n李文浩指何同學當時內心雖然驚慌，但仍強作鎮定，不理會警員的威嚇，保持面無表情，期間有警員疑因此不滿，大聲喝令他要露出笑容，他只好敷衍應對，警方最終亦沒有控告他襲警或搶槍。李認為警員的行為離譜及過份，旨在威嚇被捕人，何同男亦對警方做法亦感「好嬲」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，何同學於警署期間曾短暫致電父親，告知對方自己鼻子及下體遭警方拳擊，李文浩代何同學澄清，指因致電時間短暫未能詳述過程，其鼻子並非被拳打，而是在他面向牆壁搜身時，被警員大力推他的後腦，令他鼻子撞牆受傷流血，他其後要求送院驗傷，醫生亦證實他鼻腔內有血跡。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2789059014513034/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2789059014513034%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1PzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=4b4805ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2789059014513034/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"577aeb9d9321c9334bf94e3cb9b91852ec73fc47","tid":1829154,"uid":46170,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"告番d 黑po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚人影就唔好出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596194db0884cd2596496aeb2e3bb416e502b77c","tid":1829154,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"577aeb9d9321c9334bf94e3cb9b91852ec73fc47","tid":1829154,"uid":46170,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"告番d 黑po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚人影就唔好出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"可惜法律已經偏幫佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37330df6e12c79aba670287d5e5e2f79da420836","tid":1829154,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警煽動市民搶佢槍<br />\n求pin</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eexlIPAE0Jo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeexlIPAE0Jo&d=hCh8nFxZocjAH0BHn0nK1PzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=72fb35ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eexlIPAE0Jo</a>"},{"pid":"713624e11cf08be5834b995a4f22144b1f99b99f","tid":1829154,"uid":82746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3wbsw1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3wbsw1.jpg&h=50b77a42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"222ab0abbbe6a976c77c4991a61369778a2fa35d","tid":1829154,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53f4dAb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53f4dAb.gif&h=755d7b56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b043d32335f856ae185346bf0e7de2ce01f0ce44","tid":1829154,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcac61bc888a6b333321d8c1cce9663792ef087","tid":1829154,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T16:58:32.000Z","msg":"唔撚使講,紅底狗官會鳩判"},{"pid":"28a3bc2b0b4c697e2d793af30d5cfdd5bf9e01bb","tid":1829154,"uid":114875,"like":